{"tid":31053,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"胡楓收工車羅蘭返歸：希望傳吓緋聞","createTime":"2016-12-09T12:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T22:56:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad12e5ef01c421f3e19698ad59bb8102f12c976f","tid":31053,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"胡楓（修哥）出席品牌大獎頒獎禮，近排忙於拍攝《老表，畢業喇！》的他透露，好開心有工作做，初期拍攝家庭戲要到凌晨兩、三點先收工， 但不覺辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n家人千叮萬囑叫修哥不要駕車，擔心他駕車掛住思考，他說：「返電視城咁遠，唔駕車唔得。我依家收工會載埋羅蘭，她家是我必經之路，因為劇中跟她演夫妻好多場口一齊拍。（不怕傳緋聞？）咁多年無緋聞，希望傳吓啦！」"},{"pid":"673dff60c900f7c9186bf2c1c5b339de57651c4a","tid":31053,"uid":3510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b95a4f1b3c4fdc0e7aea1ca1ebfb0e9bc35fe6","tid":31053,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"諗起職安真漢子同毛舜筠發老姣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7028cd1d5812f8b97c5218fa685176ba006f61ee","tid":31053,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98a865f47937cc87415d63ef377e4a55b898436","tid":31053,"uid":11950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:38:23.000Z","msg":"好襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45eed4c4f4ed3535e397d26d2ca95095630d082e","tid":31053,"uid":36701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:41:01.000Z","msg":"修哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a50fef40d77cbb06b768c99862dcc45069ecb17","tid":31053,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T21:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg